title: The Cell Phone Game
itunes:title: The Cell Phone Game
itunes:subtitle: The Creepypasta Anthology
description:
The internet is filled with games and challenges that kids play, often with disastrous results. How far would you go to have control over life and death? What would you do if you couldn't turn it off?

***

Please consider supporting the podcast at Patreon.com/Creepypod or creepypod.com/support

***

Guest narration by Nichole Goodnight and Owen McCuen 

***

Produced by Steve Blizin

***

Title music by Alex Aldea

***

Intro/Outro Narration by Joe Stofko
